<hw>A*roint"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To drive or scare off by some
exclamation.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Whiskered cats
<xex>arointed</xex> flee.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Mrs. Browning.</au>⟦br⟧
